The system integrates **SHAP (SHapley Additive exPlanations)** to provide:

- Top 5 contributing risk factors  
- Domain-wise contribution percentages  
- Transparent justification for referral  

Ensures:
- Ethical AI compliance  
- Transparency  
- Government trust  
- Field-level usability  

